channel.title: Server status help (move if needed)
channel.description: If this is the wrong section, sorry. I have been a member for a while and i quit hosting a server last year, I have recently started hosting a new one and my ip is still the same. my question is can you reset the votes on my server or delete the ad so i can make a new one. the had is at 50% uptime and it has been for the last year. thanks

item.title: Server status help (move if needed)
item.dc:creator: @Flame3 John
item.description:
@Flame3 wrote:

A server isn’t removed from the server status page until its uptime drops below 40%, at which point it is removed automatically. Advertisements aren’t deleted from the server status page unless they aren’t server advertisements or are duplicate advertisements.

Read full topic
